  ('social-worker-moex-04173', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-111-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於「行政（administration）」、「管理（management）」與「治理（governance）」三者意涵的 差異，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["行政的行為主體是公部門，治理是公私部門的協力", "行政的意識形態偏重新右派的主張，管理則強調左派的社會民主觀點", "治理的使用者角色是公民而非案主", "管理的供給取向重視效率／產出，治理則重視效能／影響"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce38bf0a4fd9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad6a3199dde2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-04174', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-111-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '就規劃（planning）的意涵與目的而言，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["規劃可以因應組織環境的變遷，降低不確定性風險", "規劃使組織員工重視整體目標，減少資源重疊與浪費", "規劃階段所設定的目標，是控制階段檢視績效的基礎", "針對組織全面性、長期性的計畫，是屬於作業性規劃的成果"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce38bf0a4fd9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad6a3199dde2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-04175', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-111-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '策略性規劃（strategicplanning）的過程中，除進行SWOT分析以擬定適當策略外，亦經常運 用「PEST」的架構來評估組織外部環境，此分析架構的內涵不包含下列何者？', '["經濟的", "文化的", "社會的", "政治的"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce38bf0a4fd9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad6a3199dde2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-04176', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-111-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '領導（leadership）係指領導者帶領組織成員或團隊邁向目標的過程。下列有關領導者權力來 源的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["強制權（coercivepower）係指強迫別人服從的權力", "參照權（referentpower）係指擁有的資訊愈多、愈重要且擁有者少，則權力愈大", "法定權（legitimatepower）係指領導者擔任組織的某項職位而擁有的權力", "專家權（expertpower）係指伴隨專業、特殊技術或知識而擁有的影響力"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce38bf0a4fd9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad6a3199dde2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-04177', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-111-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關古典學派管理理論，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["科學管理學派創始者韋伯（MaxWeber）被尊稱為「科學管理之父」", "科學管理假設，將人視為「經濟人」", "員工想要的是簡易工作和財務報酬", "手藝工作者僅從事簡單工作"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce38bf0a4fd9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad6a3199dde2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-04178', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-111-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在當代領導觀點中，轉換型領導（transformationalleadership）強調以「4Is」之作為來領導部 屬，下列何者不屬於上述之「4Is」？', '["理想的（願景和價值）影響力（idealizedinfluence）", "形象管理（imagemanagement）", "激勵（學習和創新）動機（inspirationalmotivation）", "知識啟發（intellectualstimulation）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce38bf0a4fd9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ad6a3199dde2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
